    <title>Hexo博客部署到coding</title>
    <url>/posts/3879619812/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><!-- build time:Thu May 28 2020 14:49:20 GMT+0800 (GMT+08:00) --><a id="more"></a><h4 id="一、注册"><a href="#一、注册" class="headerlink" title="一、注册"></a>一、注册</h4><p>首先去<a href="https://e.coding.net/signup" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官网</a>进行注册，也可以用第三方微信进行注册<br><img src="/posts/3879619812/signup.png" alt="image"></p><h4 id="二、创建新项目"><a href="#二、创建新项目" class="headerlink" title="二、创建新项目"></a>二、创建新项目</h4><p><img src="/posts/3879619812/37V12BXHV%5DUE_~MA$1~OJ60.png" alt="image"><br>选择第三个DevOps项目后，会出现下面的页面：<br><img src="/posts/3879619812/0MGJO%5D8R4MT@5T2D4BPPX(6.png" alt="image"></p><h4 id="三、添加公钥"><a href="#三、添加公钥" class="headerlink" title="三、添加公钥"></a>三、添加公钥</h4><p>右上角头像，点击<strong>个人设置</strong><br><img src="/posts/3879619812/05KMT%7B@@MD4B_X%5BJD%7BY(R3T.png" alt="image"><br><img src="/posts/3879619812/A2LXUGVBCBJ0NAIXNS$UH%7DO.png" alt="image"><br>公钥内容在本地的 <code>C:\Users\你的账户名\.ssh</code> ，用文本编辑器打开 <code>id_rsa.pub</code> ，将里面的内容复制粘贴到此处即可。<br>如果不存在，可以再创建一个新的SSH key</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="BASH"><figure class="iseeu highlight /bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"your_email@example.com"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><div class="note warning"><p>引号里面填你的邮箱</p></div><p>然后复制你的项目地址<br><img src="/posts/3879619812/T7%7B%5DEPQO537_3%5BFBMTDV96M.png" alt="image"><br>在博客根目录下的 <code>_config.yml</code> 找到 <code>deploy</code> ，然后配置</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="BASH"><figure class="iseeu highlight /bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy: </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo:</span><br><span class="line">    github: https://github.com/liangfengg/liangfengg.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">    coding: https://e.coding.net/liangfengg/liangfengg.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>部署：</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="BASH"><figure class="iseeu highlight /bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>然后打开你的coding项目管理页，进行静态网站构建<br><img src="/posts/3879619812/A$$6K6FX.png" alt="image"><br><img src="/posts/3879619812/JH772%60TZGJ5Q@~%5BNBR_LFDD.png" alt="image"><br>点击保存，进入下一个页面：<br><img src="/posts/3879619812/3PCA84%7B4WY(GW1WC9ZX(3YW.png" alt="image"><br><img src="/posts/3879619812/KQWRQ65QM5.png" alt="image"></p><h4 id="四、绑定域名"><a href="#四、绑定域名" class="headerlink" title="四、绑定域名"></a>四、绑定域名</h4><p>点击上图右上角的设置<br><img src="/posts/3879619812/1YQ3K%7DYE@@$I0BLXXOBQBX2.png" alt="image"></p><!-- rebuild by neat -->]]></content>
